parameters:
I may be exaggerating a bit, but I still think
that meeting her was a miracle.

At that time, she was what you would call a
'street musician'. I happened to find her in front
of a station during a business trip, and I spent a
year trying to woo her... or rather, I invited her
to join Odawara Pro.

She, who was just a raw talent, is now a prominent
artist of Odawara Pro, our flagship artist, and
the public has started to recognize her.

She possessed an overwhelming singing ability that
could adapt to various musical styles. And her
beauty, which shone even more on stage, captivated
the eyes of the people multiple times over.
However... fate had bestowed upon her three
things.

\n<Audience members>Neon-sama!!, Whoaaa!!, Neon-samaaa!!, Kyaaa, Neon-
samaa\I[12], Neon-samaaa~!!, Uaaaahhh!! Neon-
samaaa~!!

She had a natural charisma... It was something she
was born with.

That's why sometimes I think... Even if I hadn't
found her, she would have become something
amazing.

And that, on an even bigger stage befitting her,
by a larger production...

......Every time I watch her live, I am reminded.
I, as an ordinary person, must work even harder
than her so that I won't be left behind by her
ever-increasing radiance.

I... felt a definite sense of fulfillment, but at
the same time, I also felt a sense of unease and
impatience due to that.

After \.\SE[ typed the \SE[ typewriter, \. typed
the \SE[ typewriter...
